{
  "stem": "22869.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they paid everything in cash, no matter what the price was that my father asked, no bargaining, nothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And from this time on, for some reason-- it must be upon the misery of the other countries-- we started to do much better than we ever did before.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because the minute my father got that money, we ran right away and we replenished our stock, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they kept coming back every few weeks, and so forth, and buying the whole thing over and over.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And it became such a-- a interesting deal, that we started believing that from now on we were going to be rich.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So we had a stable in our, like, backyard where, when I was younger, we used to have a couple of cows and a horse, and so forth, which was discontinued by now.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So we converted this to-- if you can picture-- a little automatic bottling of wine place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we installed some oven there, because we had to cook the wine, in order to pasteurize it, and so it shouldn't spoil.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we started bottling wine now, because we knew that the Germans will come, with [INAUDIBLE] labels.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we really felt good about, for the first time in our life-- little did we know that it-- that this is all happening on the misery of others.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But that's-- that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That we have now something to look forward-- we're really going to become upper middle class people, because things were going real well.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the Germans came in?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We spoke German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father and I, all our whole family, we spoke fluently German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In general?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, in school, when I went to public school, I speak-- I spoke Slovakian.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
